# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Design IP — NOT distributed in the repo. Working copies stay on disk locally;
# git history is preserved (these were untracked via `git rm --cached`, not
# purged). The product wiki at crates/xvision-dashboard/wiki/ is separate and
# stays tracked. docs/strategies/ is embedded into the xvn binary — keep it.
# (Placed last so it overrides the earlier !/docs/superpowers/ re-include.)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/docs/design/
/docs/design-audit/
/docs/testnft/
/docs/superpowers/designs/
/docs/superpowers/evidence/2026-05-24-chat-rail-dspy-strategy-agents/chat-rail/unified-stream-dashboard.png
/frontend/prototype/
/marketing/

# Build hygiene — stale npm lockfile (pnpm-lock.yaml is canonical) + generated research scratch
/frontend/web/package-lock.json
/docs/research/.gen/

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Ship only the in-app wiki + app runtime — exclude ALL internal documentation.
# Untracked via `git rm --cached` (history preserved); working copies stay local.
# KEPT (build/runtime, not ignored): docs/strategies/ (include_dir!),
# /strategies/ (seed strategy library — Dockerfile.deploy COPYs it to /strategies
# and docker/entrypoint.sh seeds it into $XVN_HOME/strategies at startup),
# crates/**/prompts/** + data/examples/README.md (include_str!), the in-app wiki
# crates/xvision-dashboard/wiki/, README.md, CHANGELOG.md, CREDITS.md, LICENSE.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/docs/*
!/docs/strategies
/team/
/decisions/
/qa/

